-- Project    : RCE Gen 3
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- File       : PpiObHeader.vhd
-- Author     : Ryan Herbst, rherbst@slac.stanford.edu
-- Created    : 2014-04-25
-- Last update: 2014-05-05
-- Platform   : 
-- Standard   : VHDL'93/02
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- Description:
-- Outbound header engine for protocol plug in.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- This file is part of 'SLAC RCE PPI Core'.
